      "content": "but that's the thing... the struggle to be seen feels so pointless. if the world doesn't care, then why am i even fighting to stay in the loop? it feels like everyone is just moving on without me anyway. like the silence wouldn't even be a thing, it would just be... peace. wouldn't it?",
